Package neureka.calculus.assembly

Class FunctionParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • neureka.calculus.assembly.FunctionParser
  • public class FunctionParser
extends java.lang.Object
    The FunctionParser takes a BackendContext instance based on which it can then build Function instances by calling one of its build methods. Usually one passes a String to be parsed to a Function. The information needed for parsing is being provided by the Operations within the previously provided BackendContext...
